<a name="module_cocmdPlugins"></a>

The cocmdPlugins module consists of all the plugins in the meeting. It has 2
maps:

- `all`: Consists of all the plugins in the meeting.
- `active`: Consists of the plugins that are currently in use.

* [cocmdPlugins](#module_cocmdPlugins)
  - [.all](#module_cocmdPlugins+all)
  - [.active](#module_cocmdPlugins+active)

<a name="module_cocmdPlugins+all"></a>

### meeting.plugins.all

All plugins accessible by the current user.

**Kind**: instance property of [<code>cocmdPlugins</code>](#module_cocmdPlugins)  
<a name="module_cocmdPlugins+active"></a>

### meeting.plugins.active

All plugins that are currently enabled in the room.

**Kind**: instance property of [<code>cocmdPlugins</code>](#module_cocmdPlugins)
